<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NPO Radio 2 Frequenties</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #22282E;
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        .contact-box {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: black;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
            min-height: 300px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

            .contact-box:hover {
                background-color: #f8d7da;
                transform: translateY(-5px);
            }

            .contact-box h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
                font-weight: bold;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

        .contact-btn {
            background-color: #D32F2F;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

            .contact-btn:hover {
                background-color: darkred;
            }

        .contact-box img {
            width: 100px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid #D32F2F;
            padding: 8px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

            ul li {
                margin: 5px 0;
            }

        .container {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .row {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                font-weight: bold;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .header p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <h1>Ontdek de Frequenties van NPO Radio 2</h1>
        <p>Luister naar de beste muziek op de juiste frequentie in jouw regio.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 d-flex">
                <div class="contact-box w-100">
                    <h2>FREQUENTIES</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Friesland: 88.0 MHz en 92.9 MHz</li>
                        <li>Groningen: 88.0 MHz</li>
                        <li>Drenthe: 88.0 MHz</li>
                        <li>Overijssel: 88.0 MHz en 104.6 MHz</li>
                        <li>Gelderland: 88.2 MHz, 92.6 MHz en 104.5 MHz</li>
                        <li>Flevoland: 88.0 MHz en 92.6 MHz</li>
                        <li>Utrecht: 92.6 MHz</li>
                        <li>Noord-Holland: 92.6 MHz en 92.9 MHz</li>
                        <li>Zuid-Holland: 92.6 MHz</li>
                        <li>Zeeland: 92.6 MHz en 97.8 MHz</li>
                        <li>Noord-Brabant: 88.2 MHz en 92.6 MHz</li>
                        <li>Limburg: 88.2 MHz, 93.4 MHz en 97.2 MHz</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="#" class="contact-btn">Bekijk meer frequenties</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
